data.description: Seller will contribute up to $5,000 in buyers closings costs or rate buy down. Beautifully updated rare find in the heart of Crestview. Split yet open floor plan with oversized rooms and 2 living rooms. Detached unfinished garage in the back yard. Lots of space inside the home and in the yard for entertaining, featuring a brand new privacy fence. Lawn equipment could remain with a full price offer.
